da je možda ovo stenoviti
put pre nečega

464
00:44:36,451 --> 00:44:39,587
novog i divnog.

465
00:44:45,263 --> 00:44:47,964
Ali ne bih prihvatila taj skok.

466
00:44:49,167 --> 00:44:52,270
