Je li ovo u tebi? Reci mi.

527
00:52:13,854 --> 00:52:16,153
Uzmi ovo... napiši.

528
00:52:16,500 --> 00:52:18,072
Reci mi sve.

529
00:52:18,790 --> 00:52:20,471
Napiši, hajde.

530
00:52:21,238 --> 00:52:22,238
